ViewHolder for DatabasesAdapter

* lockImg - ImageView representing whether database is opened or closed
* databaseName - TextView which holds database name
* menu - 3 dots menu

init constructor:
* initializes all properties above
* sets onClickListener on itemView that obtains view position (using getAdapterPosition)
  and navigates to OpenDatabaseFragment passing through obtained position
  Note: it may notify DatabasesPresenter about click and DatabasesPresenter
  should navigate to OpenDatabaseFragment
